data.description: Impeccable 2 story, 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths pool - jacuzzi! Home located in the desirable community of Calusa Corners. Features a warm open appointed kitchen plan w/gas cook top, lots of wooden cabinets & closets for storage, vaulted wooden ceilings in the family w/wet bar, water salt softener, lots of upgrades w/plenty of room for entertaining, yet still cozy enough for any family. Upstairs large master bedroom w/wooden floors, walking closet w/ a balcony overlooking at pool area. Exterior features a fabulous backyard with an authentic Argentinian style grill barbecue, pool & a separate jacuzzi. Incredibly well kept home with many features to list. Won't last. Good morning: SELLER’S FINANCING ON CASH BUYER’S ONLY. DINING TABLE CRYSTAL CHANDALIER from living & dining not include in sale.
